Sai Pallavi is more Talented & Beautiful than those bollywood folks â¤

Nani is such an underrated actor, we give all the unnecessary focus to the biggest commercial movies and overlook such gems. I watched Ante Sundaraniki and there's a scene in the climax that is so heart touching, I dont think I have seen an actor down south doing a crying scene so effortlessly apart from Fahadh Faasil, Dhanush, Jr NTR in recent times, really deserves lot more attention even from the Bollywood biggies, make this man fmaous, give him his long due credit. Sai Pallavi is on a different league altogether, no other pan Indain actress can do what she's doing, she's truly gifted. She can pull of a Fida and do Vacchinde, she can do a Maari and give us the most viewed south indian song on Youtube, she can play a Rosie/Devdaasi and perform classical dance rotuines and be convincing at it, she can do a Virata Parvam where she is a naive village girl madly in love with a naxalite and eventually become one, she can also become a Gargi, I mean look at her Projects, so diverse and all the characters are so deeply rooted that its difficult to not relate to her. Lots of love and best wishes to these talented bunch of people who make our lives so enriched through their craftsmanship. I am in awe through and through.
